title: VMWare ESX: Number of Virtualmachnies and Hostssystems
agents: vsphere
catalog: os/misc
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This Check only counts the nubmer of Virtualmachines on a Hostsystem, or the number of
 Virtualmachines and Hostsystems on a vCenter.
 Via the rule "Distribution of virtual machines over ESX hosts" you can make sure that a
 given set of VMs is running on a given number of different Hosts.

discovery:
 One service is created.
